OL,6,FFinnich Glen, known for its 70ft gorge
OL,7,Fand the Devil's Pulpit rock, has been
OL,8,Fused as a backdrop for films and TV
OL,9,Fshows, ITV News Scotland Correspondent
OL,10,FPeter Smith reports
