OL,3,CScottish filming location Devil's
OL,4,CPulpit up for sale amid safety concerns
OL,6,FFinnich Glen, known for its 70ft gorge
OL,7,Fand the Devil's Pulpit rock, has been
OL,8,Fused as a backdrop for TV shows
OL,9,FOutlander, Taggart and Sherlock
OL,10,FHolmes, as well as films including The
OL,11,FEagle and Detective Pikachu.
OL,13,FWith it's name in the spotlight, it
OL,14,Fhas received an influx of tourists
OL,15,Fwith an estimated 70,000 people a year
OL,16,Fvisiting the glen.
OL,18,FBut this has left the ground in poor
OL,19,Fcondition while some visitors put
OL,20,Fthemselves at risk to take photographs
OL,21,Fof the famous terrain.
