OL,3,CScottish filming location Devil's
OL,4,CPulpit up for sale amid safety concerns
OL,6,FLandowner David Young, whose family
OL,7,Fhas owned the gorge since the 1940's,
OL,8,Fsays he hopes a new owner can improve
OL,9,Fthe safety of the site.
OL,11,F"What we want to do is make sure
OL,12,Fpeople can come here, get a good
OL,13,Fexperience and do it safely, being the
OL,14,Fkey point," he told ITV News.
OL,16,FMr Young added there had been a few
OL,17,Faccidents over the years due to the
OL,18,Fconditions.
