OL,4,CPulpit up for sale amid safety concerns
OL,6,FWhile there is no exact price-tag on
OL,7,FFinnich Glen, estate agent Peter
OL,8,FSeymor, of Graham + Sibbald, said it
OL,9,Fcould sell for a "seven-figure sum."
OL,11,FThe 23-acre site on the banks of the
OL,12,Fgorge, are being marketed with
OL,13,Fplanning permission for a visitor
OL,14,Fcentre, restaurant, cafe, shop and
OL,15,Fevents area, as well as a car park for
OL,16,F150 vehicles.
OL,18,FThe number of visitors is predicted to
OL,19,Frise to 350,000 if a visitor centre
OL,20,Fwas erected.
