OL,6,FMr Young added: "There is an
OL,7,Fopportunity here at Finnich Glen to
OL,8,Fcreate a visitor attraction of
OL,9,Fnational importance.
OL,11,F"It is indeed a beautiful Scottish
OL,12,Flandmark that is visited by people
OL,13,Ffrom all around the world - it has
OL,14,Fbeen previously referred to as
OL,15,FScotland's Grand Canyon in miniature."
